The paper deals with the problem of drug recommendation and adverse drug reaction prediction, which involves machine learning and data analysis techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) categories. Additionally, the paper involves the development of a joint model and the use of real datasets, which suggests that it may also belong to the Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE) and Databases (cs.DB) categories. Finally, the paper involves information retrieval techniques for evaluating the performance of the model, which suggests that it may also belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) category.
